high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right at the counter to the right of the fridge.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn around, go forward to the counter to the right of the sink.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn around, go forward and left to the fridge.
Put the knife on the top shelf of the fridge.
Turn around, go back to the counter with the lettuce.
Take a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Go left to the sink.
Wash the slice of lettuce in the sink then take it out.
Turn around, go forward and left to the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge in front of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of washed lettuce in a fridge.

high_descs: Go to the counter to the right of the fridge
Grab a knife off of the counter
Turn around and go to the counter to the right of the sink
Slice the lettuce on the counter
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn around and go to the counter to the right of the sink
Grab a slice of lettuce off the counter
Turn left and stop at the sink
Wash the sliced lettuce in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the sliced lettuce in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting clean sliced lettuce in the fridge

high_descs: Turn right and head to the counter next to the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the lettuce on the counter.
Cut the lettuce into several slices.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the knife on the top shelf in the fridge and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk back to the counter with the lettuce.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Take a step to the left to stand in front of the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn right, walk past the counter, and turn right towards the fridge,
Place the slice of lettuce in front of the tomato inside the fridge and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife along with a washed slice of lettuce in the fridge.
